American singer, actor Tyrese Gibson and his wife Samantha Lee Gibson landed in South Africa on Tuesday. The actor shared his excitement to be in the country on his Instagram page. He has been posting pictures and videos of him and his wife in Johannesburg. “Johannesburg, South Africa here’s my first post. I can’t believe I am here, unreal times to come,” Gibson captioned a video.  As the Fast and Furious star shares his time in the country on his timeline, he also shared moments with his wife having private lunch with the former first lady of South Africa Winnie Madikizela Mandela. Gibson posted a number of beautiful, heartwarming pictures and videos of their time with Madikizela Mandela.  -TNA Reporter  